Subject: Allow Electron visibility for CDM renderer

patch-reason: 2

electron needs //electron visibility on components/cdm/renderer to

build cdm renderer integration; this is electron-specific.

Patch-Dir: src/electron/patches/chromium
Patch-Filename: allow_electron_visibility_for_cdm_renderer.patch
(cherry picked from commit 57e4348470829642d8c1a2150ab1266d6d6614b8)
---
 components/cdm/renderer/BUILD.gn | 1 +
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+)

diff --git a/components/cdm/renderer/BUILD.gn b/components/cdm/renderer/BUILD.gn
index fbe2ec2264cd1..614bb127acc01 100644
--- a/components/cdm/renderer/BUILD.gn
+++ b/components/cdm/renderer/BUILD.gn
@@ -14,6 +14,7 @@ static_library("renderer") {
     "//components/cdm/*",
     "//content/shell/*",
     "//fuchsia_web/*",
+    "//electron/*",
   ]
 
   sources = [
